description:
I worked on creating the iOS companion app for a banking solution. The technology of choosing was SwiftUI with the idea that it would be suited for creating future macOS and iPad versions.
The main challenges included going through the Apple Pay process, direct client communication, leading a team of 5 people, conducting technical trainings for new employees;
The solution is used in Allianz Bulgaria Mobile Banking and BNCTL Mobile Banking;
Responsible for: mobile solution architecture, team task management, demos, mentoring;

Team lead for frontend teams, total of 9 people and responsible for the developed web and mobile solutions;
Hiring manager and conducting technical interviews;
Developing the main architecture used in both React JS and React Native apps;
Developing new support tools for the development process like Design Tool or Translation Tool. They are developed as cli apps, webpack plugins, VSCode plugins, directly communicating with Jenkins;
My main goal was to create an environment for all future projects to be created and maintained, and for new features to be implemented with ease;
Responsible for: creating UX, solution architecture, team task management, creating dev ops tools, presentations/demos, team expansion, mentoring, planning and preparing for eventual scenarios, remote problem solving;
